snippet: Charl Schwartzel shot a 66 to put him at nine under par and give him a one-shot lead on a fellow South African, Zander Lombard, heading into the final round of the Tshwane Open in Pretoria, South Africa.
lead_paragraph: Charl Schwartzel shot a 66 to put him at nine under par and give him a one-shot lead on a fellow South African, Zander Lombard, heading into the final round of the Tshwane Open in Pretoria, South Africa.

headline.main: Charl Schwartzel Has Narrow Lead in Tshwane Open
